        <Parent_String>scales (rules) [300225200], rulers by function [300225558], rulers (measuring devices) [300266529], linear distance measuring devices [300198750], distance measuring devices [300195705], measuring devices for extent [300195701], measuring devices (instruments) [300207870], Measuring Devices (hierarchy name) [300207851], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
